⍝ OuterProduct.tc
⍝ ═══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: RO dyadic function; LO is jot (∘)
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (⍴A),⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ (⍴⍴A)+⍴⍴B
      A ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,3) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← A ∘.× B
      (⍴Z) ≡ (⍴A),⍴B
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,(⍴⍴A)+⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: (I,¨J)⊃Z ←→ (I⊃A) RO J⊃B  — use bracket form
      Z[2;3] ≡ (2⊃A)×3⊃B
1
